<h3>
<a id="getting-the-latest-release" class="anchor" href="#getting-the-latest-release" aria-hidden="true"><span class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>Getting the latest release</h3>

<p>JALSE <a href="https://github.com/Ellzord/JALSE/releases">releases</a> and (SNAPSHOTs) are published to maven central (<a href="http://search.maven.org/">http://search.maven.org/</a>).</p>

<p>Example for Maven:</p>

<div class="highlight highlight-xml"><pre>&lt;<span class="pl-ent">dependency</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span class="pl-ent">groupId</span>&gt;com.github.ellzord&lt;/<span class="pl-ent">groupId</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span class="pl-ent">artifactId</span>&gt;JALSE&lt;/<span class="pl-ent">artifactId</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span class="pl-ent">version</span>&gt;1.0.6&lt;/<span class="pl-ent">version</span>&gt;
&lt;/<span class="pl-ent">dependency</span>&gt;</pre></div>

<p>Example for Gradle:</p>

<pre><code>compile 'com.github.ellzord:JALSE:1.0.6'
</code></pre>

